{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a7b8c9d0-e1f2-3456-7890-abcdef123456",
    "name": "Smart Licitaciones — Verificación Release",
    "description": "Colección única para **confirmar todos los cambios del backend** antes de subir a producción.\n\n**Requisitos:** API en marcha, `npm run seed:ubicaciones`, migraciones 001 y 003, entorno **Smart Licitaciones — Local**.\n\n**Ejecutar:** Collection Runner → carpeta **▶ RUN — Verificación completa** → Run.\n\n**Cubre:** PERF-004/007, TRX-006, CLI-004, CON-003, PRY-014, FEC-001/005, carga masiva (3 entidades), operador país fijo.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "try {",
          "  const body = pm.response.json();",
          "  if (body.devActivationToken) pm.environment.set('activationToken', body.devActivationToken);",
          "  if (body.preAuthToken) pm.environment.set('preAuthToken', body.preAuthToken);",
          "  if (body.accessToken) {",
          "    const reqName = (pm.info.requestName || '').toLowerCase();",
          "    if (reqName.includes('operador')) pm.environment.set('operadorAccessToken', body.accessToken);",
          "    else pm.environment.set('accessToken', body.accessToken);",
          "  }",
          "  if (body.usuario?.id) pm.environment.set('targetUserId', String(body.usuario.id));",
          "  if (body.cliente?.id) pm.environment.set('clienteId', String(body.cliente.id));",
          "  if (body.contacto?.id) pm.environment.set('contactoId', String(body.contacto.id));",
          "  if (body.proceso?.id) pm.environment.set('procesoId', String(body.proceso.id));",
          "  if (body.parametro?.id) pm.environment.set('parametroId', String(body.parametro.id));",
          "  if (body.proyeccion?.id) pm.environment.set('proyeccionId', String(body.proyeccion.id));",
          "  if (body.data?.[0]?.id && pm.request.url.path.join('/').includes('ubicaciones')) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('ubicacionId', String(body.data[0].id));",
          "  }",
          "} catch (e) {}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "▶ RUN — Verificación completa",
      "description": "Ejecutar en orden con Collection Runner. Todos los tests deben pasar.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "01. GET Health",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const ts = Date.now();",
                  "pm.environment.set('adminCorreo', `admin-release-${ts}@local.test`);",
                  "pm.environment.set('operadorCorreo', `operador-release-${ts}@local.test`);",
                  "pm.environment.set('empresaCarga', `Empresa Release ${ts}`);",
                  "pm.environment.set('anioParametro', String(2000 + (ts % 50)));"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"] }
            }
          ],
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health" }
        },
        {
          "name": "02. POST Crear Admin (paisId obligatorio)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Admin-Dev-Key", "value": "{{adminDevKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Admin Release\",\n  \"correo\": \"{{adminCorreo}}\",\n  \"rol\": \"Administrador\",\n  \"paisId\": {{paisId}}\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/users"
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["pm.test('201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));", "pm.test('paisId', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().usuario.paisId).to.eql(Number(pm.environment.get('paisId'))));"] } }]
        },
        {
          "name": "03. POST Activar Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{activationToken}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/activate"
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"] } }]
